How to Run:
•
Backend: Run the Spring Boot app via your IDE or terminal:
Shell Script
./gradlew :backend:bootRun
•
Frontend: Start the development server:
Shell Script
./gradlew :frontend:jsBrowserDevelopmentRun --continuous
This will start a server (usually at localhost:8080 or similar) and automatically reload when you make changes to the Kotlin code in frontend/src/jsMain/kotlin.

Create executable via: gradle launcher:createExe